Dialogue: 3,0:21:51.00,0:21:55.29,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}那就都塞到瓶子裡
Dialogue: 3,0:21:55.88,0:21:58.42,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}準備好參加派對了嗎?
Dialogue: 3,0:21:58.42,0:22:00.42,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}不等你了哦
Dialogue: 3,0:22:00.96,0:22:04.47,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}另一個故事就要開始了
Dialogue: 3,0:22:05.18,0:22:07.35,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}無數氣泡呼呼冒出
Dialogue: 3,0:22:07.47,0:22:09.60,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}無數氣泡啵啵破裂
Dialogue: 3,0:22:09.85,0:22:13.19,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}生活就像汽水
