Dialogue: 3,0:22:18.73,0:22:23.07,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}都會化作氣泡消失掉
Dialogue: 3,0:22:23.57,0:22:25.66,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}哭泣憂愁又煩惱
Dialogue: 3,0:22:25.86,0:22:27.87,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}無數往事多紛擾
Dialogue: 3,0:22:28.16,0:22:31.58,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}都沒關係的
Dialogue: 3,0:22:32.25,0:22:34.75,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}所有往事盡懷抱
Dialogue: 3,0:22:34.75,0:22:37.00,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}塞進瓶子使勁搖
